","tag-manners-adab","tag-prophetic-virtues-manaqib-nabawi","tag-supplication-al-dua"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-5ct","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":23,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2010\/09\/11\/rahmah-compassion-for-children\/","url_meta":{"origin":19993,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Mercy: The Prophet is merciful to his children","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 11, 2010","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: Al-Aqra' ibn Habis saw the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, kissing his grandson Al-Hasan. He said, \u201cI have ten children and I do not kiss any of them.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cVerily, whoever does not show mercy will not receive mercy.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5997,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13481,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/10\/hasan-ibn-ali-makes-peace\/","url_meta":{"origin":19993,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Hasan: The Prophet\u2019s grandson Hasan ibn Ali makes peace","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 10, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Bakrah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThis grandson of mine is a master. Perhaps Allah will reconcile two groups of Muslims through him.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2557 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0628\u064e\u0643\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7570,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/03\/o-allah-be-merciful-to-them\/","url_meta":{"origin":19993,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Children: O Allah, be merciful to them as I am merciful","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 3, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Usamah ibn Zayd reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would put me on one of his thighs and he would put Hasan ibn Ali on his other thigh. Then, the Prophet would hug us and he would say, \u201cO Allah, be merciful to them as\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28834,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/08\/hasan-husayn-two-sweet-basils\/","url_meta":{"origin":19993,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Husayn: Hasan and Husayn are my two sweet-basils","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 8, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abi Nu\u2019m reported: I watched Ibn Umar, may Allah be pleased with him, as he was asked about a man killing mosquitoes. Ibn Umar said, \u201cWhere are you from?\u201d The man said, \u201cThe people of Iraq.\u201d Ibn Umar said, \u201cLook at this man! He asks me about killing mosquitoes\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9897,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/22\/ali-ibn-abi-talib-harun-musa\/","url_meta":{"origin":19993,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Prophets: Ali is to Muhammad as Aaron to Moses","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 22, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019d ibn Abi Waqqas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, set out to Tabuk and he left Ali behind. Ali said, \"You leave me behind with the women and children?\" The Prophet said, \"Are you not pleased in the same position for me as Aaron\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7625,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/04\/dawah-hidayah-islam-better\/","url_meta":{"origin":19993,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Da&#8217;wah: Guiding a person to Islam better than all wealth","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 4, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Sahl ibn Sa\u2019d reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBy Allah, that Allah guides a man through you is better for you than a herd of expensive red camels.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3009, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2406 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\